<reference id="adoption-interview-questionnaire">
  <title>Adoption Inquiry Form – Cerberus</title>
  <shortdesc>
  This form is an optional adoption interview questionnaire. Please answer all questions and attach the requested photos to help us ensure a good match.
  Submit your adoption request at https://rehome.adoptapet.com/adopters/application/4702523/step-1 and for a guide on how to submit an adoption form, check out the <xref href="Task-How-to-Adopt-Cerberus.xml">How to Adopt Cerberus guide</xref>.
  </shortdesc>

  <refbody>
    <section>
      <title>How to Complete and Submit This Questionnaire</title>
      <p>Print your answers directly in this form. You may include photos of current pets or family members. </p>
      <p> Save the completed questionnaire and email it along with your photo attachments to: christinaemayr@gmail.com with the subject line "Adoption Interview Questionnaire – Cerberus".
      </p>
      <p>Include the Following Details in Your Email Message:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Your full name and location (city, state)</li>
        <li> Short introduction</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <title>Applicant Details</title>
      <ul>
        <li>Full name: ___________________________________________________________________________________</li>
        <li>Email address: ___________________________________________________________________________________</li>
        <li>Phone number: ___________________________________________________________________________________</li>
        <li>City and state/province: ___________________________________________________________________________________</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <title>Home and Household</title>
      <ul>
        <li>Type of home (apartment, house, etc.):</li>
        <li>Do you have a yard? Is it fenced?</li>
        <li>How many household members live with you (names and ages)?</li>
        <li>Do you currently have any other pets? If so, list species, breed, and age:</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <title>Experience and Lifestyle</title>
      <ul>
        <li>Have you owned dogs before? If yes, describe your experience:</li>
        <li>Have you ever had a high-energy or working breed dog?</li>
        <li>What is your daily schedule like? How long would Cerberus be alone at home?</li>
        <li>Who will be primarily responsible for his training and care?</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <title>Motivation and Questions</title>
      <ul>
        <li>Why are you interested in adopting Cerberus?</li>
        <li>Do you have any concerns or questions about his care, behavior, or training?</li>
        <li>Are you willing to commit to a trial period and post-adoption follow-ups?</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <title>Photo Attachments</title>
      <p>Attach the following photos to the email with your completed form:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Photos of your home (inside) and yard (if applicable)</li>
        <li>Photos of other pets currently in the home</li>
        <li>Optional: Photos of family members who live with you</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </refbody>
</reference>
